<div class="home-v2-new" id="homev2"><div class="hv2-bg" id="hv2bg"></div><div class="hv2-decor"><span class="orb"></span><span class="ring"></span><span class="leaf"></span><span class="mist"></span><span class="mist"></span><span class="mist"></span></div><header class="hv2-top"><a href="/en/" class="hv2-brand"><img src="/assets/images/logo.webp" alt="O2F life"><span>O2F life</span></a><nav class="hv2-links"><a href="#programs">Programs</a><a href="#results">Results</a><a href="#plans">Plans</a><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Start Now</a></nav></header><nav class="hv2-dock" aria-label="Home V2 quick navigation"><a href="#hero" class="active">Home</a><a href="#programs">Programs</a><a href="#results">Results</a><a href="#plans">Plans</a><a href="#stories">Stories</a><a href="#contact">Start</a></nav><main class="hv2-main"><section class="hv2-section hv2-hero" id="hero"><div><span class="kicker">Coach Osama Omran — O2F.life</span><h1>Transform your body, from the inside out.</h1><p>Personalized coaching that combines training, nutrition, anti-aging direction, and performance follow-up in one clear transformation journey.</p><a class="hv2-btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Start your transformation</a></div></section><section class="hv2-section compact" id="intro"><div class="split"><article class="panel glass"><span class="kicker">The full system</span><h2>A science-driven, nature-backed approach.</h2><p>O2F brings coaching, nutrition direction, performance habits, anti-aging guidance, and transformation follow-up into one clear premium journey.</p><p>The experience is simple: choose your path, see the result system, compare plans, and start.</p><a class="hv2-btn" href="#programs">Explore the system</a></article><div class="photo glass"><img src="/assets/images/hero.jpeg" alt="Coach Osama Omran"><div class="stats"><span>20+<br><small>Years</small></span><span>1000+<br><small>Clients</small></span><span>100%<br><small>Custom</small></span><span>24/7<br><small>Support</small></span></div></div></div></section><section class="hv2-section" id="programs"><div><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">Choose your path</span><h2>Three focused routes inside one transformation system.</h2><p>Anti-aging, Methylene Blue education, and training transformation are grouped as premium glass tabs to keep the page compact, clear, and impressive.</p></div><div class="tabs-shell glass"><div class="tabs-nav" role="tablist"><button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="anti" type="button">Anti-Aging</button><button class="tab-btn" data-tab="blue" type="button">Methylene Blue</button><button class="tab-btn" data-tab="training" type="button">Training Transformation</button></div><article class="tab-panel active" id="tab-anti" data-theme="anti"><div class="tab-copy glass"><span class="kicker">Longevity direction</span><h3>Age with better energy, recovery, and daily performance.</h3><p>A clean route for vitality, recovery habits, smarter lifestyle routines, and long-term wellness follow-up.</p><div class="benefit-grid"><div class="benefit"><b>Recovery</b><span>Sleep, stress load, and routine control.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Vitality</b><span>Nutrition and habits that support daily energy.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Consistency</b><span>Simple follow-up that keeps the plan realistic.</span></div></div><div class="mini-journey"><span>Assess lifestyle</span><span>Build routine</span><span>Track progress</span></div></div><div class="tab-visual glass"><span class="visual-icon">A+</span></div></article><article class="tab-panel" id="tab-blue" data-theme="blue"><div class="tab-copy glass"><span class="kicker">Cellular energy</span><h3>Methylene Blue presented as a clear performance education route.</h3><p>A premium simple section around focus, energy, cellular performance, and proper professional guidance.</p><div class="benefit-grid"><div class="benefit"><b>Focus</b><span>Positioned around mental clarity and alertness.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Energy</b><span>Explains the cellular performance concept visually.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Guidance</b><span>Directs visitors to safe professional consultation.</span></div></div><p class="note">Guidance-first approach. Ask before starting.</p></div><div class="tab-visual glass"><span class="visual-icon">MB</span></div></article><article class="tab-panel" id="tab-training" data-theme="fit"><div class="tab-copy glass"><span class="kicker">Body transformation</span><h3>Training, nutrition, and follow-up built around your body and lifestyle.</h3><p>A structured route for fat loss, muscle gain, athletic shape, and long-term body transformation.</p><div class="benefit-grid"><div class="benefit"><b>Training</b><span>Goal-based workout planning.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Nutrition</b><span>Food direction that fits daily life.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Follow-up</b><span>Adjustments based on real progress.</span></div></div><div class="mini-journey"><span>Assess</span><span>Plan</span><span>Transform</span></div></div><div class="tab-visual glass"><span class="visual-icon">FIT</span></div></article></div></div></section><section class="hv2-section compact" id="results"><div class="results-grid"><div class="before-after glass"><div class="ba-card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517838277536-f5f99be501cd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=85" alt="Before transformation"><span class="ba-label">Before</span></div><div class="ba-card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605296867304-46d5465a13f1?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=85" alt="After transformation"><span class="ba-label">After</span></div></div><div class="result-copy"><article class="stat-card glass"><strong>3x</strong><p>Clearer progress tracking through structured follow-up.</p></article><article class="stat-card glass"><strong>12</strong><p>Weeks to build a visible transformation rhythm.</p></article><article class="stat-card glass"><strong>1</strong><p>One connected system for training, nutrition, and lifestyle.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="hv2-section compact" id="plans"><div class="plans-wrap"><div><span class="kicker">Plans</span><h2>Choose the level that matches your goal.</h2><p>Each plan has a clear subscribe button so visitors understand the next step immediately.</p><a class="hv2-btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Start with guidance</a></div><div class="plans-grid"><article class="plan glass"><span class="kicker">Starter</span><h3>Basic Plan</h3><p>Simple start with training and nutrition direction.</p><ul class="features"><li>Training direction</li><li>Nutrition guidance</li><li>Progress points</li></ul><a class="plan-btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Subscribe now</a></article><article class="plan glass highlight"><span class="kicker">Most popular</span><h3>Standard Plan</h3><p>Balanced option for stronger follow-up.</p><ul class="features"><li>Training plan</li><li>Nutrition direction</li><li>Weekly adjustments</li></ul><a class="plan-btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Subscribe now</a></article><article class="plan glass"><span class="kicker">Advanced</span><h3>Premium Plan</h3><p>Detailed follow-up and premium support.</p><ul class="features"><li>Full transformation plan</li><li>Detailed monitoring</li><li>Lifestyle optimization</li></ul><a class="plan-btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Subscribe now</a></article></div></div></section><section class="hv2-section compact" id="stories"><div><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">Real voices</span><h2>Comments that make the decision easier.</h2><p>Short, direct proof cards keep the page human and build confidence before the final action.</p></div><div class="comments"><article class="comment glass"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><h3>Clear and easy</h3><p>The plan felt organized and realistic. I knew exactly what to do every week.</p></article><article class="comment glass"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><h3>Visible progress</h3><p>The follow-up made the difference. The plan changed when my body changed.</p></article><article class="comment glass"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><h3>Premium guidance</h3><p>Training, nutrition, and support were all connected in one simple system.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="hv2-section" id="contact"><div class="contact-grid"><article class="panel glass"><span class="kicker">Start now</span><h2>Ready to start your transformation?</h2><p>Choose your path and let O2F guide your next version with a clear plan, visual progress, and direct support.</p><a class="hv2-btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Contact and subscribe</a></article><div class="faq"><article class="bubble glass"><b>Is this only training?</b><p>No. It combines training, nutrition, and ongoing follow-up.</p></article><article class="bubble glass"><b>Not sure where to start?</b><p>Send your goal and current level, then the right route can be selected.</p></article><article class="bubble glass"><b>What makes it different?</b><p>It is built around your goals, schedule, lifestyle, and current level.</p></article></div></div></section></main></div><script>(function(){var root=document.getElementById('homev2');var bg=document.getElementById('hv2bg');var tabs=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn'));var panels=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.tab-panel'));var dock=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.hv2-dock a'));var sections=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.hv2-section[id]'));function fx(){var max=root.offsetHeight-window.innerHeight||1;var p=Math.max(0,Math.min(1,-root.getBoundingClientRect().top/max));root.style.setProperty('--scroll',Math.round(p*1000));bg.style.setProperty('--bg-x',(Math.sin(p*4)*24)+'px');bg.style.setProperty('--bg-y',(-p*260)+'px');bg.style.setProperty('--bg-scale',(1.14+p*.08).toFixed(3));root.style.setProperty('--light-y',(-p*120)+'px');var current=sections[0];sections.forEach(function(s){var r=s.getBoundingClientRect();if(r.top<window.innerHeight*.45&&r.bottom>window.innerHeight*.2){current=s;}});dock.forEach(function(a){a.classList.toggle('active',a.getAttribute('href')==='#'+current.id);});}tabs.forEach(function(btn){btn.addEventListener('click',function(){var target='tab-'+btn.getAttribute('data-tab');tabs.forEach(function(b){b.classList.toggle('active',b===btn);});panels.forEach(function(p){p.classList.toggle('active',p.id===target);});});});dock.forEach(function(a){a.addEventListener('click',function(e){var el=document.querySelector(a.getAttribute('href'));if(el){e.preventDefault();el.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'start'});}});});window.addEventListener('scroll',fx,{passive:true});window.addEventListener('resize',fx);fx();})();</script>
